title: OnePlus rolls out March 2022 patches to OnePlus Nord, Nord N200, and Nord N10 5G
content:
Last week, OnePlus rolled out the March 2022 security patches to the OnePlus 9, OnePlus 9 Pro, and OnePlus 9RT. The company is now giving a similar treatment to three more devices: OnePlus Nord, Nord N200, and Nord N10 5G. The original OnePlus Nord is receiving an update to OxygenOS 11.1.10.10. It’s a minor update

The post OnePlus rolls out March 2022 patches to OnePlus Nord, Nord N200, and Nord N10 5G appeared first on xda-developers.
